# shadcn/ui — Installation

Install a new component:
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]
```

Examples: `button`, `card`, `input`, `dialog`, `dropdown-menu`, `select`, `badge`, `toast`

Already installed components are in `src/components/ui/`. Check there first before installing.
